<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276529>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52 – 57. Rogicka joannae n. sp., MZUSP 0 304 (holotype specimen), off São Paulo, Brazil. 52, Colony with ovicell; 53, close-up of autozooid; 54, close-up orifice. 55, close-up of frontal wall, note the single pores; 56, autozooid with several distal spines; 57, close-up of distal spines." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

